<doc>
  <member name="D3D11_SHADER_TYPE">
    <summary>
      <para>Identifies a shader type for tracing.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>
        <b>D3D11_SHADER_TYPE</b> identifies the type of shader in a <see cref="D3D11_SHADER_TRACE_DESC" /> structure.</para>
      <para>
        <b>Note</b>  This API requires the Windows Software Development Kit (SDK) for Windows 8.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d11/d3d11-graphics-reference-shader-enums">Shader Enumerations</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D11_SHADER_TYPE.D3D11_VERTEX_SHADER">
